data.description: Welcome Home! This home has fresh paint and carpet and is situated on a corner lot.  This open concept kitchen is great for meal prep and allows for great conversation and entertaining. The Primary bedroom is situated downstairs with an ensuite bathroom.  The second floor has three bedrooms and a flex room which can be used as a bedroom or Gameroom or study. The backyard has a shed as well as a covered patio great for entertainment and activities.  As you can see this home can be customized to fit the needs of it's next owner.  Will that be you?
